3	## Locking
4	
5	Rust's [`print!`] and [`println!`] macros lock stdout on every call. If you
6	have repeated calls to these macros it may be better to lock stdout manually.
7	
8	[`print!`]: https://doc.rust-lang.org/std/macro.print.html
